{"word":"Furnace","slug":"furnace","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Furnace</b> Uses of:<br/> - For refining silver<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=22'>Eze 22:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=3'>Mal 3:3</a> <br/> - For refining gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=17&verse=3'>Pro 17:3</a> <br/> - For melting lead and tin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=20'>Eze 22:20</a> <br/> - For capital punishment, Shadrach, Meshach, and Abed-Nego cast into, by Nebuchadnezzar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=26'>Dan 3:26</a> <br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of affliction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=20'>Deu 4:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=51'>1Ki 8:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=12&verse=6'>Psa 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=48&verse=10'>Isa 48:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=11&verse=4'>Jer 11:4</a> <br/> - Of lust<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=4'>Hos 7:4</a> <br/> - Of hell<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=4&verse=1'>Mal 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=42'>Mat 13:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=50'>Mat 13:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=2'>Rev 9:2</a> "}]}